{"first_name":"Richard","last_name":"Howe","permalink":"richard-howe","crunchbase_url":"http://www.crunchbase.com/person/richard-howe","homepage_url":"http://richardkhowe.com","birthplace":"Montreal","twitter_username":"richardkhowe","blog_url":"http://inuvo.com/blog/introducing-ceo-connection-richard-k-howe","blog_feed_url":"","affiliation_name":"ieWild","born_year":null,"born_month":null,"born_day":null,"tag_list":"inuvo, acxiom, fico, ceo, cmo, online-advertising, branding, advertising, marketing, data, analytics, merger, acquisition, operations, innovation, entrepreneur, hnc","alias_list":null,"created_at":"Mon Jan 19 15:20:59 UTC 2009","updated_at":"Sun Mar 18 01:30:25 UTC 2012","overview":"<p>Richard Howe is a 25 year Marketing/Operating veteran who has been on the forefront of applied online and offline information technology &amp; software designed to reduce risk, catch fraud and improve online and offline marketing results. He has been a C-level executive and board member in companies ranging in size from start-up through billions in annual revenue across 3 continents.</p>\n\n<p>Rich is currently the Executive Chairman of micro-cap public Internet marketing technology innovator, Inuvo, Inc. (INUV), which he recently merged with internet consumer software pioneer, Vertro, Inc. (VTRO). </p>\n\n<p>Previously, Richard was Chief Marketing, M&amp;A and Business Strategy Officer at public mid-cap marketing services leader, the Acxiom Corporation (ACXM) where in addition to his other responsibilities, he operated about $300M of the companies P/L.</p>\n\n<p>Prior to Acxiom, Rich was the General Manager of the $110M annual revenue marketing services division of public mid-cap analytics &amp; software powerhouse, Fair Isaac Corporation (FIC).  </p>\n\n<p>Before joining Fair Isaac, Rich founded and was the founder &amp; CEO of private internet search pioneer, ieWild Inc., which he sold to HNC Software, a public company (HNC)  innovator of fraud technology and software where he had worked in both sales and product leadership capacities. </p>\n\n<p>Rich has been involved in more than 10 M&amp;A transactions to $800 million with the majority of those companies information technology oriented with online business models.</p>\n\n<p>Rich graduated first in his class with a Bachelor’s degree in engineering along with a Master’s degree from McGill University, Canada. Rich is a patented inventor and has sat on the boards of a number of non-profit organizations. </p>\n\n<p>Rich has been a Marketing, Sales, Operations, Technology and M&amp;A executive on the forefront of innovation for 25 years as a senior leader in businesses ranging in size from startup through $1.2 billion in annual revenue in countries that include USA, Canada, UK, Australia and China.</p>","image":{"available_sizes":[[[120,150],"assets/images/resized/0003/4796/34796v2-max-150x150.jpg"],[[165,206],"assets/images/resized/0003/4796/34796v2-max-250x250.jpg"],[[165,206],"assets/images/resized/0003/4796/34796v2-max-450x450.jpg"]],"attribution":""},"degrees":[{"degree_type":"Bachelor's Degree","subject":"Engineering ","institution":"Concordia University","graduated_year":null,"graduated_month":null,"graduated_day":null},{"degree_type":"Master's","subject":"Engineering","institution":"McGill University","graduated_year":null,"graduated_month":null,"graduated_day":null}],"relationships":[{"is_past":false,"title":"Chief Executive Officer","firm":{"name":"Inuvo","permalink":"inuvo","type_of_entity":"company","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,59],"assets/images/resized/0003/2025/32025v8-max-150x150.jpg"],[[250,98],"assets/images/resized/0003/2025/32025v8-max-250x250.jpg"],[[450,177],"assets/images/resized/0003/2025/32025v8-max-450x450.jpg"]],"attribution":null}}},{"is_past":true,"title":"Chief Executive Officer ","firm":{"name":"ieWild","permalink":"iewild","type_of_entity":"company","image":null}},{"is_past":true,"title":"Chief Marketing & Business Strategy Officer","firm":{"name